---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="关于本编辑部" description="About 海外住宿编辑部">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-primary mb-8">关于本编辑部</h1>
    <div class="font-body text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <p>中国留学生海外住宿决策站（公寓/宿舍/homestay 横评 + 区域指南）</p>
      <p class="mt-4">This is an independent editorial site. We are not affiliated with any institution mentioned unless explicitly disclosed. Content is researched and written for informational purposes.</p>
      <p class="mt-4">Contact: <code>contact@unistay.cn</code></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>